CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Station wagon inscribed "Regular Democratic Endorsed Candidates; For Governor - David L. Lawrence, For U.S. State Senator - George M. Leader, For State Legislature - K. Leroy Irvis, Jas. F. Clarke - 1st, 3rd, 4th, 5th & 16th Wards", another version
